Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.76,0:00:08.16,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Once there was a man who obtained everything,\Nthe legendary Pirate King Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.16,0:00:12.71,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,His last words before he was executed inspired people to sail the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.71,0:00:14.43,Gold,Roger,0,0,0,,All my wealth and treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.43,0:00:16.07,Gold,Roger,0,0,0,,It can be yours if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.07,0:00:17.22,Gold,Roger,0,0,0,,Search for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.22,0:00:19.59,Gold,Roger,0,0,0,,I left everything in that one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.59,0:00:22.62,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,People now set sail in search of romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.62,0:00:25.20,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The world has entered a Great Age of Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:31.67,Main,Voice,0,0,0,,Ryuuguu Palace!  Ryuuguu Palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:33.63,Main,Voice,0,0,0,,This is the Border Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.63,0:02:37.42,Main,Voice,0,0,0,,An enormous shipwreck is requesting emergency entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.14,0:02:38.62,title,Voice,0,0,0,,The Shipwrecked Celestial Dragon!\NA Bullet that Seals the Future
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.60,0:02:41.38,Main,Right Minister,0,0,0,,What are you doing?! \NNaturally, you have to let them in{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.38,0:02:42.93,Main,Voice,0,0,0,,If I'm not mistaken...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.14,0:02:49.35,Main,Voice,0,0,0,,a Celestial Dragon is onboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.70,0:02:50.89,Main,Right Minister,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:53.23,Main,Right Minister,0,0,0,,King Neptune!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:55.19,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,A Celestial Dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.19,0:02:56.54,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,Grant him access!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:02:58.90,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,Send an emergency unit to the coast!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:02:59.39,Main,Guards,0,0,0,,Yes, Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:01.91,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,I will be there shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:02.79,Main,Right Minister,0,0,0,,Otohime-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:07.25,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,What business does a Celestial Dragon have on the ocean floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.92,0:03:10.70,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,A Celestial Dragon's ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.70,0:03:13.16,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,It looks like it was attacked by a deep sea creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.16,0:03:19.21,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,What business do Celestial Dragons,\Nwho discriminate against us, have on the ocean floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.41,0:03:22.17,Main,Myosgard,0,0,0,,Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.31,0:03:28.56,Main,Myosgard,0,0,0,,Damn it!  Those spineless cowards all died on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:32.06,Main,Myosgard,0,0,0,,Hurry and bring me a mask, you pathetic fish-creatures!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:36.42,Main,Myosgard,0,0,0,,This place reeks of fishmen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:41.94,Main,Myosgard,0,0,0,,Hurry and bring me a mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:45.67,Main,Myosgard,0,0,0,,Save my life, you imbeciles!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:48.62,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Just how self-centered...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:50.95,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Is that really the attitude\Nsomeone asking for help should have?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.91,0:03:55.28,Main,Myosgard,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:57.96,Main,Myosgard,0,0,0,,Get me a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.54,0:03:59.45,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,Where's the medical team?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.45,0:04:01.16,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,They're here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.16,0:04:03.21,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,they're not sure what to do about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.21,0:04:05.03,Main,Hody,0,0,0,,We should kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.72,0:04:10.17,Main,Hody,0,0,0,,The worst type of trash in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:16.52,Main,Vander Decken,0,0,0,,There sure is a lot of noise coming from the port.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.87,0:04:17.49,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.33,0:04:23.98,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Captain, apparently a Celestial Dragon has come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.98,0:04:26.16,Main,Vander Decken,0,0,0,,A Celestial Dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:29.96,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Seems he got here on a wrecked ship,\Nand he's now asking for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.76,0:04:32.64,Main,Vander Decken,0,0,0,,Sounds interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:34.54,Main,Vander Decken,0,0,0,,Let's go take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:42.49,Main,Myosgard,0,0,0,,This wasn't supposed to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.07,0:04:47.72,Flashbacks,Myosgard,0,0,0,,What? My fishman slaves\Nhave returned to Fishman Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:49.97,Flashbacks,Myosgard,0,0,0,,Why did that happen, My Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.57,0:04:52.93,Flashbacks,His Daddy,0,0,0,,From what I hear, My Son,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:58.15,Flashbacks,His Daddy,0,0,0,,the latest addition to the Seven Warlords of the Sea\N was a fishman named Jinbe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:04:59.82,Flashbacks,Myosgard,0,0,0,,Jinbe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:05.16,Flashbacks,His Daddy,0,0,0,,The slaves who fled and joined the Sun Pirates,\Nwhich he was a part of,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:08.89,Flashbacks,His Daddy,0,0,0,,were given a pardon by the Government, forgiven for the sin of running away,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.89,0:05:12.16,Flashbacks,His Daddy,0,0,0,,and returned to their country, it seems, My Son.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:17.88,Flashbacks,Myosgard,0,0,0,,I'm sure that the slaves that ran away from my house\Nare among them, My Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:20.62,Flashbacks,His Daddy,0,0,0,,They must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.62,0:05:25.76,Flashbacks,His Daddy,0,0,0,,When I think about how they must be living\Nsuch carefree lives right now, I get really annoyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:29.64,Flashbacks,Myosgard,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll go get them back, My Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:34.14,Flashbacks,Myosgard,0,0,0,,My fishman slave collection,\Nthat I spent so much money gathering!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.42,0:05:39.23,Main,Myosgard,0,0,0,,Damn it... I didn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.43,0:05:42.54,Main,Myosgard,0,0,0,,that the deep seas were this terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:45.43,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Hey!  What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:05:59.47,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Long time no see, Myosgard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.47,0:06:02.89,Main,Myosgard,0,0,0,,You dare address me without honorifics... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.68,0:06:10.34,Main,Myosgard,0,0,0,,Oh, you are... my slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:13.94,Main,Myosgard,0,0,0,,Obediently come back to my home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.94,0:06:16.44,Main,Myosgard,0,0,0,,Who gave you permission to be free,\Ndamn fish-creatures?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.74,0:06:25.71,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,S-Stop it, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:29.66,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,He's a Celestial Dragon!\NLay a hand on him, and your pardons will be void!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.21,0:06:33.17,Main,Myosgard,0,0,0,,Stop it, you fool!  Know your place!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.17,0:06:36.05,Main,Myosgard,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea who I am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.05,0:06:38.47,Main,Myosgard,0,0,0,,I am... I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.47,0:06:44.36,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Up on the surface, a Navy Admiral will immediately be dispatched if a Celestial Dragon is harmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.36,0:06:47.27,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,That's the only reason why everyone fears you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.10,0:06:51.38,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,However, this is Fishman Island, on the bottom of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.38,0:06:55.91,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,As long as the citizens here keep quiet, it won't matter what happens to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:57.44,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,It'll just be assumed you had an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.57,0:07:00.42,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:02.72,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,I won't say a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.72,0:07:03.92,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Neither will I!  Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:08.81,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,He's barely alive anyway!\NHe'll die if we just ignore him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.81,0:07:12.42,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Let him taste the pain you had to endure as slaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.42,0:07:13.53,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:14.93,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Let him suffer, and kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:16.27,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Don't forgive him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.86,0:07:20.05,Main,Myosgard,0,0,0,,What?  I am great...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.73,0:07:22.22,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Even if I wanted to forgive...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.23,0:07:33.32,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,You're the one person I could never forgive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.42,0:07:36.39,Main,Myosgard,0,0,0,,Hey, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.87,0:07:38.02,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:38.89,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.89,0:07:45.07,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.07,0:07:46.99,Main,Myosgard,0,0,0,,Damn fish-creatures!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:04.75,Main,Fishmen,0,0,0,,{\i1}Queen Otohime!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.37,0:08:10.81,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Her Majesty's been shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.36,0:08:22.97,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Queen Otohime...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.42,0:08:27.35,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,Everyone... Please throw away your guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.75,0:08:31.69,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,The children are watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:41.07,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,Aladdin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.73,0:08:44.23,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,What's this I heard\Nabout a shipwrecked Celestial Dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:46.04,Main,Aladdin,0,0,0,,I only just got here myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.85,0:08:48.75,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,Boss Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.37,0:08:52.72,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,Mother raced out of the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:53.97,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:57.68,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Big Brother, who are these Celestial Dragons?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:09:00.32,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,They're humans, Shirahoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.32,0:09:01.35,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.44,0:09:07.57,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,Out of all the humans in the world, they're among the scariest ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.57,0:09:11.12,Main,Aladdin,0,0,0,,I heard several gunshots.  Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.12,0:09:11.95,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:13.59,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Otohime-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.37,0:09:17.31,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,It only grazed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.31,0:09:18.95,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Why did you protect him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:22.54,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Do you know what that man did to us in the past?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:29.05,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,He treated us worse than slaves, even worse than cattle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:33.66,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,I can hear the screams of\Nyour hearts so clearly, it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.95,0:09:37.30,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.31,0:09:38.53,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.19,0:09:46.31,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,I know it must be difficult for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:50.17,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,but your anger and hatred toward the humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.17,0:09:52.57,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,Do not pass it on to the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.54,0:09:58.41,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,Think of what they must face from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.98,0:10:06.19,Flashbacks,Tiger,0,0,0,,So, I beg of you! {Copy-paste from 543}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.19,0:10:10.17,Flashbacks,Tiger,0,0,0,,Don't tell the people on our island anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:15.34,Flashbacks,Tiger,0,0,0,,Not about the tragedy that befell us,\Nnor about our anger towards the humans. {End copy-paste from 453}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.54,0:10:18.72,Thoughts,Jinbe,0,0,0,,Brother Ti...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:22.29,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Look out, Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.54,0:10:25.90,Main,Myosgard,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.90,0:10:27.70,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,Oh no!  Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.78,0:10:32.16,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.54,0:10:33.45,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:10:59.27,Main,Fishmen,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sea Kings?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:29.01,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,What... was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.59,0:11:31.68,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,It couldn't just be a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:39.75,Thoughts,Otohime,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi... You couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.96,0:11:46.84,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:51.23,Thoughts,Decken,0,0,0,,There is a legend passed down in my family...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:59.31,Thoughts,Decken,0,0,0,,In the distant past, there lived a Mermaid Princess\Nwho possessed the sacred power to control Sea Kings!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.31,0:12:05.58,Thoughts,Decken,0,0,0,,My forefather Vander Decken traveled to the ocean floor in pursuit of that legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.58,0:12:10.78,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,{\i1}Honored forefather!  I have finally found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.78,0:12:14.14,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi is the legendary Mermaid Princess?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:16.09,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,You did it, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.58,0:12:19.66,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,It would be bad if anyone else heard about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.66,0:12:24.88,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,This is a secret legend, that only my family knows of...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.88,0:12:26.42,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,I presume!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.42,0:12:29.58,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,If I could freely control the Sea Kings and have them do my bidding,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.58,0:12:32.16,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,everyone would have to do as I told them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.16,0:12:34.77,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,I would be able to take whatever I wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.14,0:12:38.64,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,So, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.64,0:12:40.85,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Are we going to kidnap Princess Shirahoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.38,0:12:44.65,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,First, I must become the princess's husband!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.65,0:12:46.89,Main,Fishmanz,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whaaaaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.89,0:12:49.65,Main,Fishmanz,0,0,0,,But Princess Shirahoshi is still a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.65,0:12:52.61,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,Indeed, and therein lies the problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.91,0:12:56.93,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,Aladdin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:02.21,Main,Aladdin,0,0,0,,I will... treat his wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.33,0:13:05.19,Main,Aladdin,0,0,0,,And yours as well, Otohime-sama, as soon as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:12.22,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,Some weeks later, after the Celestial Dragon's treatment was complete and his life had been saved,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:14.58,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,and he was about to leave for his homeland...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.58,0:13:18.89,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,Queen Otohime made an astonishing move.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.48,0:13:32.39,Main,Myosgard,0,0,0,,Remember this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.39,0:13:37.70,Main,Myosgard,0,0,0,,All the tactlessness and rudeness that I, a World Noble, had to endure here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:41.47,Main,Myosgard,0,0,0,,Damn fish-creatures!\NI swear I will make you regret them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.10,0:13:45.27,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,We saved his life, so why does he resent us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.27,0:13:50.85,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,Our country gave him\Nthe ship and crew to take him home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:52.53,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,How can he talk to us like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.53,0:13:57.18,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,We shouldn't let him leave.\NHe'll just put the island in even greater danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:00.79,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,Please, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.75,0:14:03.95,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,We still have some unfinished business, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.50,0:14:07.55,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,That being the case,\NI will accompany you to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.51,0:14:09.80,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,To the surface?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:11.68,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,That's crazy!  Otohime-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:12.97,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.38,0:14:15.53,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,Wait -jamon, Otohime!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.53,0:14:17.75,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,I will not allow you to do something so self-centered!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:21.81,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,If you absolutely must settle things with the Nobles, then I will go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:28.36,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,You are the king and a great knight,\NI'm sure you'd never be captured by the humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:29.78,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,That's why it should be me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.78,0:14:33.24,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,No.  If someone as strong as you went,\Nit would be meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:39.33,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,If the weak cannot travel there and return safely,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:43.57,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,we cannot prove to our citizens that the surface is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:48.42,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,That is why I, who am weaker than most,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.42,0:14:50.42,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,must go to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.51,0:14:52.88,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.88,0:14:53.76,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:14:55.40,Main,Fishkid,0,0,0,,Otohime-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.40,0:14:57.86,Main,Fishkid,0,0,0,,Are you going somewhere, Otohime-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:01.60,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,Otohime...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:02.99,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,Believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.53,0:15:07.16,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,in the wife you chose, and in the humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.33,0:15:16.35,Main,Myosgard,0,0,0,,She's merely the queen of\Nthese fish-creatures!  Such conceit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.29,0:15:24.50,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.50,0:15:27.13,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.34,0:15:32.87,Main,Aladdin,0,0,0,,Jinbe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.87,0:15:36.48,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,Nobody could have possibly stopped her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.48,0:15:39.89,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,We can only believe in her, and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.89,0:15:47.03,Main,Crowd,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your Majesty!  Please, be safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.12,0:15:47.03,Secondary,Kid,0,0,0,,Otohime-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.03,0:15:50.50,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.51,0:16:04.55,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,The Ryuuguu Kingdom was enveloped in a cycle of sleepless nights caused by uncertainty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.55,0:16:09.72,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,But there was nothing we could do except pray for the Queen's safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.48,0:16:15.02,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Japanese folklore object resembling Pandora's Box
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.48,0:16:15.02,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,What's that?  The Tamate Box?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:19.54,Main,Underling,0,0,0,,That's right, Captain!\NAmazingly enough, I hear it's in Ryuuguu Palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:22.24,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,And anyone that opens the box immediately grows old?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.24,0:16:24.62,Main,Underling,0,0,0,,That's right!  That's how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.62,0:16:29.89,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,So, for example,\Nif a little squirt like this kid were to open it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.89,0:16:32.79,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,she'd become a sexy broad\Nabove the age of consent?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.79,0:16:34.64,Main,Underling,0,0,0,,She most certainly would.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:38.39,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,Yes!  My problem is solved!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:41.39,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,Then I could quickly marry Princess Shirahoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:43.17,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,I presume!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.17,0:16:46.59,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,Go steal that Tamate Box immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.59,0:16:52.55,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,No... wait a second...\NBreaking into Ryuuguu Palace ain't so easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:55.61,Main,Underling,0,0,0,,But if you marry Shirahoshi first...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:56.98,Main,Underling,0,0,0,,then you could come and go as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:17:00.02,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,You guys sure are smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:03.02,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi ain't exactly ugly,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:07.20,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,so she should be a good looking broad in ten or twenty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.60,0:17:09.55,Main,Underling,0,0,0,,But she'll be even bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.72,0:17:13.87,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,That's even better.\NI don't have anything against big women!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.61,0:17:20.46,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,That girl is the legendary Mermaid Princess who can control Sea Kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.46,0:17:23.17,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,I will become her husband,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.17,0:17:27.93,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,and once I've gotten that power, I will finally realize...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.28,0:17:33.51,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,the dream that the Vander Decken family has sought after for generations!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.50,0:17:38.17,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,Alright, now let's get started on the wedding invitations.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.76,0:17:41.19,Main,Underling,0,0,0,,Proposing comes first!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.19,0:17:43.69,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,Oh!  I don't have any friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.82,0:17:47.53,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,Days passed without any news of the Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.53,0:17:50.70,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,The uncertainty just grew and grew.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.70,0:17:53.04,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Man, I even miss her speeches.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.91,0:17:58.87,Thoughts,Fishwoman,0,0,0,,Please, somehow, come back alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.87,0:18:02.66,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,Hey, Boss, where's Otohime-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.66,0:18:03.80,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,When's she coming back?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.80,0:18:06.30,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,Have faith in her and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.30,0:18:11.05,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,She set out on this journey for the sake of {\i1}your{\i0} future.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.43,0:18:17.52,Thoughts,Jinbe,0,0,0,,Your Highness, please be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:25.86,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.08,0:18:38.37,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,It's fine -jamon.  Believe in her and wait -jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.63,0:18:44.22,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,A week passed, which felt like 100 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.11,0:18:48.92,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.84,0:19:03.37,Main,Citizens,0,0,0,,Hooray!  Otohime-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.84,0:19:07.68,Main,Ministers,0,0,0,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.38,0:19:13.05,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Just knowing that she's alive... We're so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:15.14,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.14,0:19:17.32,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Your Highness...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.91,0:19:20.85,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,It took several days to persuade them,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.85,0:19:25.28,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,but Queen Otohime finally calmed the Celestial Dragons...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:28.85,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,and the sheet of paper that she brought back...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.57,0:19:33.91,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,could be called the light of hope for Fishman Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.76,0:19:38.30,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,Attention everyone!\NThe World Nobles have a lot of political power...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:43.98,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,when it comes to the Council of Kings, and even the World Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.98,0:19:48.51,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,This was written by a World Noble.\NHere's what it says:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.51,0:19:51.68,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,"For peace and friendship between fishmen and humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.20,0:19:57.06,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,I hereby endorse\Nthe proposal of the attached petition."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.06,0:20:01.70,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,In other words, when we submit\Nall of our signatures to the World Council Meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.70,0:20:08.24,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,by including this single piece of paper we will have actual power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:11.07,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,We will definitely be able to emigrate to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.07,0:20:13.83,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,The Celestial Dragons are backing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.83,0:20:14.70,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Politics is complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.70,0:20:19.59,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,All we have to do\Nis to collect a large number of signatures...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.59,0:20:24.29,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,so the final decision is yours.\NI can only wait while you decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:27.46,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,How about it?  Live alongside the humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.46,0:20:31.05,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,Please indicate your desire to emigrate to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:36.34,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,Please!  Your signatures!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:54.18,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,Children, aren't you just trying to make me happy,\Nonly to ask to take them back later?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.18,0:20:57.68,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,Nope!\NMom said she's gonna submit one, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.96,0:21:22.99,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Otohime-sama.  This small box just ain't big enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.99,0:21:25.59,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Just how many people do you think are in this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:31.40,Main,Minister of the Right,0,0,0,,That's right!  Start using this box, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.75,0:21:35.86,Main,Minister of the Right,0,0,0,,Put your signatures into this box\Nto say that you support the Queen's burning dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.12,0:22:07.08,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,Fishmen and humans.  We're turning\Nour eyes away from the history of segregation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.97,0:22:14.51,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,But, it was the Queen's decision to take\Nthose first bold steps that gave birth to this hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.08,0:22:18.40,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,If we can gather just a few more signatures,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.40,0:22:22.57,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,we might really change Fishman Island's future.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.00,0:22:26.94,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,If he'd been touched\Nby Queen Otohime's burning conviction,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.94,0:22:30.74,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,even Arlong might have been saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.50,0:22:37.58,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,I wish Brother Ti could have seen this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.61,0:22:49.84,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,It was at that moment...\Nwhen I gained the courage to truly change this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:22:50.86,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,That moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.97,0:22:55.43,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,Yes, the day when the Sea Kings peeked in on Fishman Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.63,0:22:58.71,Main,Manboshi,0,0,0,,I think everyone was surprised that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.67,0:23:02.47,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,They came because Shirahoshi called them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.47,0:23:03.26,Main,Princes,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.26,0:23:07.92,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,All fishmen are capable of\Ncommunicating their feelings to fish,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.92,0:23:10.20,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,so we're certainly able to talk to them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.01,0:23:17.04,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,But not just anyone can talk to those great Sea Kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.73,0:23:24.63,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,Even the only person capable of communicating with whales, your father, Neptune, can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.63,0:23:28.49,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,There is a legend that is passed down\Nthrough the royal family.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.49,0:23:36.09,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,Every few hundred years, a mermaid will be born with the ability to communicate with Sea Kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.09,0:23:38.23,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,Those humongous Sea Kings?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.23,0:23:39.50,Main,Manboshi,0,0,0,,You're talking about Shirahoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.39,0:23:45.26,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,That's right.  Someday, someone capable of guiding her power to be used for the right purpose will appear,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.26,0:23:52.48,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,and this will bring about a great change to the world.  Or so the legends say.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.48,0:23:53.77,Main,Manboshi,0,0,0,,The whole world?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.18,0:23:59.04,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,If that's true, I'm sure that great changes will occur on this island too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.04,0:24:02.23,Main,Ryuuboshi,0,0,0,,So, maybe that power will assist your efforts?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.23,0:24:03.24,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.24,0:24:09.51,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,If you want to save people, it's a power of love capable of saving thousands of lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.51,0:24:13.83,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,But if a dark-hearted person were to wield it,\Nthey could sink the whole world under the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.32,0:24:17.71,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,One of the most terrifying powers in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.39,0:24:22.59,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,She still hasn't realized that she wields this power,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.59,0:24:24.47,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,and she can't control it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.88,0:24:29.71,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,If Shirahoshi experiences another shock, even greater than the one before,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.71,0:24:35.28,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,she may unconsciously\Nsend the Sea Kings on a rampage.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.78,0:24:39.17,Main,Ryuuboshi,0,0,0,,If that happens,\NFishman Island could be turned into rubble!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.17,0:24:40.37,Main,Ryuuboshi,0,0,0,,What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.37,0:24:44.82,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it now.\NI'll figure something out eventually, so it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.82,0:24:50.25,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,For now, the three of you should concentrate on\Ngrowing up and becoming magnificent warriors.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.66,0:24:58.63,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Please, as big brothers and as warriors, you must protect your little sister with your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.63,0:24:59.50,Main,Ryuuboshi,0,0,0,,I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.50,0:25:00.26,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.97,0:25:02.22,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.62,0:25:08.28,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,But then the incident happened, without any warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.81,0:25:15.98,Main,Warrior,0,0,0,,Get back!  They're going up in flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.98,0:25:18.23,Main,Warrior,0,0,0,,How did the signature box suddenly catch fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.23,0:25:19.07,Main,Warrior,0,0,0,,Water!  Get water!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.07,0:25:20.57,Main,Warrior,0,0,0,,Quickly, put the fire out!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.57,0:25:21.86,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,How could this happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.86,0:25:23.99,Main,Minister of the Right,0,0,0,,After all the effort we went through to collect the signatures!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.17,0:25:46.37,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Otohime-sama's been shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.37,0:25:47.54,Main,Aladdin,0,0,0,,Who the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.54,0:25:51.25,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,There's a sniper out there!  Protect the Royal Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.25,0:25:52.30,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.30,0:25:53.50,Main,Ryuuboshi & Manboshi,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.50,0:25:56.00,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,It's too dangerous here!\NPlease fall back to the Ryuuguu Gondola.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.00,0:25:59.13,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,Princes!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.13,0:26:02.14,Main,Miniser of the Right,0,0,0,,Your Highness!  Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.14,0:26:04.41,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Otohime-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.68,0:26:09.92,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,Hey Princess, this must be difficult for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.91,0:26:11.85,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,Who are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.85,0:26:13.19,Main,Decken,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.19,0:26:14.86,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,Don't approach the Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.86,0:26:15.93,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.53,0:26:21.66,Main,Ryuuboshi & Manboshi,0,0,0,,Mother!  Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.66,0:26:23.31,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.95,0:26:30.08,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,Dammit!  Who the hell did this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.08,0:26:32.23,Main,Miniser of the Right,0,0,0,,Why aren't the paramedics here yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.23,0:26:33.91,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,Mother!  Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.91,0:26:35.34,Main,Manboshi,0,0,0,,Open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.34,0:26:39.87,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unforgivable!\NI'll destroy whoever is responsible for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.69,0:26:43.64,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.42,0:26:52.90,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,Stay by my side, my little angels.  Don't make such scary faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.73,0:27:01.54,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,I was careless.\NAll those signatures made me so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.54,0:27:03.41,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,Truly happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.40,0:27:08.23,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,Prince Fukaboshi, I'm the one who is upset...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.23,0:27:10.16,Main,Medic,0,0,0,,Your Highness!  We're ready to treat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.37,0:27:18.25,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,So, whoever the culprit is...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.84,0:27:22.81,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,please don't be angry for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.82,0:27:31.59,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,Don't lose yourself in anger and hatred because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.54,0:27:46.41,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.95,0:27:53.63,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi.  Control yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.06,0:28:08.09,Flashbacks,Otohime,0,0,0,,If Shirahoshi experiences another shock, greater than the one before...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.84,0:28:12.71,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.30,0:28:19.95,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.96,0:28:24.29,Main,Manboshi,0,0,0,,Hey!  Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.31,0:28:39.25,Main,Manboshi,0,0,0,,Akkamanbo akamanbo!  Akkamanbo akamanbo!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.25,0:28:41.77,Main,Manboshi,0,0,0,,Look!  Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.77,0:28:43.71,Main,Manboshi,0,0,0,,Akkamanbo akamanbo!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.10,0:28:46.64,Main,Ryuuboshi,0,0,0,,It's fun!  It's fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.64,0:28:50.01,Main,Ryuuboshi,0,0,0,,There's nothing to cry about!  Let's sing, Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.65,0:28:55.28,Main,Ryuuboshi,0,0,0,,The three of us will always be here for you -la ti do!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.20,0:29:01.53,Main,Manboshi,0,0,0,,Manbo dancing sure is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.11,0:29:05.41,Main,Manboshi,0,0,0,,So fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.41,0:29:08.60,Main,Ryuuboshi,0,0,0,,Yeah!  Fun -do re mi fa!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.11,0:29:11.51,Main,Minister of the Right,0,0,0,,What are the princes doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.51,0:29:13.22,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,Stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.22,0:29:14.64,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,This isn't appropriate!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.64,0:29:18.34,Main,Manboshi,0,0,0,,Mother!  Look!  Look!  It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.80,0:29:24.78,Main,Ryuuboshi,0,0,0,,We'll always protect her like this -la ti do!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.28,0:29:30.02,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,Please stop!\NDon't you understand Her Highness's condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.66,0:29:37.48,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,Mother.  We'll recollect the burnt signatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.15,0:29:42.35,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,We'll become great soldiers like our father.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.22,0:29:50.04,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,Just as we promised,\Nwe'll protect Shirahoshi with our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.04,0:29:52.37,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,So please...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.37,0:29:57.63,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,P-Please, don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.33,0:30:06.33,Main,Otohime,0,0,0,,It's just a hair's breadth away... The light of the real sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.68,0:30:50.74,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,There he is!  We've found the assassin!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.74,0:30:53.52,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,Hurry!  Hurry to the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.89,0:30:58.19,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,Is that him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.41,0:31:01.83,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,Where is the assassin?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.83,0:31:03.27,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,Jinbe-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.27,0:31:05.31,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,We just took him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.31,0:31:07.05,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,Who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.05,0:31:08.04,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.94,0:31:13.01,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.84,0:31:18.43,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,a human?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.37,0:31:22.60,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,Don't let anyone know!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.79,0:31:24.13,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,What?  Boss Jinbe?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.52,0:31:26.31,Main,Hody,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.58,0:31:31.28,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,What would become of all of Her Majesty's efforts?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.07,0:31:34.89,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,This would destroy them completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.65,0:31:37.86,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,Isn't that just too much?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.89,0:31:43.60,Main,Hody,0,0,0,,But this is the harsh reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.60,0:31:46.00,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,No!  He's a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.83,0:31:50.54,Main,Hody,0,0,0,,Whether or not he's a pirate is irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.35,0:31:53.34,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,Don't do it, Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.34,0:31:54.50,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.43,0:32:00.51,Main,Hody,0,0,0,,Listen up, all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.39,0:32:05.19,Main,Hody,0,0,0,,A human...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.01,0:32:10.74,Main,Hody,0,0,0,,killed our country's queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.94,0:32:18.83,Main,Hody,0,0,0,,Queen Otohime's killer was human!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.10,0:32:27.65,Main,Right Minister,0,0,0,,How could this happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.36,0:32:30.72,Main,Left Minister,0,0,0,,A human.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.23,0:32:34.57,Main,Left Minister,0,0,0,,Her Majesty kept telling us to live with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.57,0:32:36.99,Main,Left Minister,0,0,0,,and moved by her words,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.99,0:32:39.06,Main,Left Minister,0,0,0,,we had decided to walk beside them.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.06,0:32:42.52,Main,Left Minister,0,0,0,,But now a human...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.52,0:32:44.21,Main,Left Minister,0,0,0,,has shattered that dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.04,0:32:50.28,Main,Left Minister,0,0,0,,He's taken the life of the person we all dearly loved!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.28,0:32:54.78,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,You may be dead, but that doesn't\Ngive us Queen Otohime back, human!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.22,0:33:00.32,Main,Left Minister,0,0,0,,Has this world been forsaken by God and Buddha alike?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.90,0:33:03.21,Main,Left Minister,0,0,0,,This is too cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.21,0:33:07.23,Main,Left Minister,0,0,0,,Far too cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.11,0:33:21.61,Main,Left Minister,0,0,0,,Is His Majesty still inside Koukaku Tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.78,0:33:25.07,Main,Right Minister,0,0,0,,Minister of the Left...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.07,0:33:27.36,Main,Right Minister,0,0,0,,It is as you hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.36,0:33:30.62,Main,Right Minister,0,0,0,,He said that he couldn't control himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.62,0:33:32.50,Flashbacks,Neptune,0,0,0,,Lock the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.50,0:33:36.94,Flashbacks,Neptune,0,0,0,,Don't open it until my bloodthirst passes!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.06,0:33:48.80,Main,Left Minister,0,0,0,,Your Majesty...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.80,0:33:50.82,Main,Left Minister,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.87,0:33:53.64,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,Minister of the Left...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.64,0:33:57.17,Main,Left Minister,0,0,0,,The culprit was still carrying a gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.17,0:33:59.98,Main,Left Minister,0,0,0,,so the soldiers shot him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.69,0:34:02.54,Main,Left Minister,0,0,0,,It was a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.60,0:34:07.56,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,I would have killed him even if he was unarmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.17,0:34:14.66,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,But I'm sure Otohime would\Nnever have forgiven me for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.10,0:34:19.42,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,I don't know when this cycle of revenge started...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.42,0:34:23.37,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,but if I had killed him,\NI'd have just been sucked into that very cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.37,0:34:27.13,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,And any children who saw it...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.13,0:34:30.75,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,would have the seed of hatred planted in their hearts,\Nso they'd also be dragged in.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.75,0:34:34.85,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,The cycle would grow even larger.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.18,0:34:40.34,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,In my head, I understand what Otohime told us.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.34,0:34:42.89,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,Or rather,\NI could if this was happening to someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.58,0:34:51.46,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,But... why can't I kill someone if they kill my wife?!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.26,0:34:56.18,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,I just don't get it -jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.28,0:35:03.83,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,I lived as a warrior\Nand avenged countless fallen comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.64,0:35:09.38,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,Many humans attacked me, and I crushed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.38,0:35:14.72,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,After all that, I didn't think I had the right to help with Otohime's campaign,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.72,0:35:17.30,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,so I just watched over her instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.30,0:35:22.69,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,Why do the innocent die... while I still keep on living?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.69,0:35:30.34,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,Even if I tried to continue Otohime's work,\NI would just look like a hypocrite -jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.27,0:35:37.58,Main,Left Minister,0,0,0,,But... peoples' hearts constantly change.\NWe are all full of contradictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.58,0:35:40.10,Main,Left Minister,0,0,0,,Both fishmen and humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.10,0:35:44.60,Main,Left Minister,0,0,0,,And there will always be things\Nthat only a warrior can protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.91,0:35:55.55,Main,Guards,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.53,0:36:02.68,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,Sorry for worrying you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.68,0:36:07.69,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,I couldn't miss my own wife's funeral -jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.86,0:36:12.14,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Father!  Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.14,0:36:13.66,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.70,0:36:23.34,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.34,0:36:25.05,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,Children...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.41,0:36:27.92,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.58,0:36:36.15,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,Forgive me... for not being here when you needed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.10,0:36:41.42,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Father, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.13,0:36:43.68,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.68,0:36:47.53,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Wherever I go, letters keep flying after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.53,0:36:50.70,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,This is the fifth one already, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.70,0:36:54.10,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,This is... a love letter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.10,0:36:56.31,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi is still only six years old!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.85,0:36:59.58,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,Who is this Vander Decken?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.58,0:37:02.52,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,He's from a family of pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.02,0:37:07.55,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,Don't let the children attend the funeral!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.55,0:37:11.70,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,The assassin might still have\Nsome allies running around.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.70,0:37:15.80,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,And as for this pirate named Decken,\Ncapture him immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.80,0:37:16.88,Main,Guards,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.14,0:37:57.68,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.17,0:37:59.51,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,The monitor...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.35,0:38:04.45,Main,Fishman,0,0,0,,Prince Fukaboshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.67,0:38:06.15,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,Fukaboshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.28,0:38:11.37,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,Just before she died,\Nour mother told us with a smile on her face...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.11,0:38:16.04,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,that the light of the real sun was just a hair's breadth away.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.72,0:38:24.02,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,We have decided to dedicate our lives to fulfilling our mother's wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.69,0:38:26.58,Main,Right Minister,0,0,0,,Princes...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.58,0:38:33.25,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,Your hearts may not heal\Nin time for the World Council Meeting in two years...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.81,0:38:38.09,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,but there's another one in six years.  And yet another in ten years!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.82,0:38:44.86,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,I'm sure you have conflicted feelings about humans following this incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.60,0:38:49.54,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,We discarded all the signatures\Nthat hadn't already burned to ash.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.69,0:38:54.94,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,Let's restart from square one!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.31,0:39:04.43,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,Someday...\Nwhen everyone's hearts have had time to heal...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.14,0:39:11.13,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,let us... dream of the sun together!
